{"word":"ποταίνιος","slug":"ποταίνιος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ποταίνιος</b></el> <el>(ποτ-αίνιος, η, ον) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ποτί  πρός, αἶνοσ?</el>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>fresh, new</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>recens</el>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>new, unexpected, unheard of</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}